&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;The information in this module was developed by the Aberdeenshire Council GIRFEC (Getting it Right for Every Child) Training Officer who has kindly allowed us to develop the original material into a Learnpro module.&#160; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

