	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;74% access the internet on their phone (raising to 76% for 11-16 year olds).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;Average age for getting a smart phone is 9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;Games consoles&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;53% of 5-10 year olds &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;63% of 11-16 year olds&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;28% play games with friends&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;13% play games with people they don&amp;apos;t know&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;tab-stops: list 36.0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;Smartphones and tablets present unique risk environments as most network level filters do not apply to applications used on such devices. However, there are some technical tools available for parents / carers. The following 3 controls are specific to app management and can help protect what children and young people can download and view online: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;tab-stops: list 36.0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;Changing the settings on a phone or tablet to stop apps being downloaded&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;tab-stops: list 36.0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;Changing the settings to prevent in-app purchases &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;tab-stops: list 36.0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;Parental control software to restrict app installation or use &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;In the study conducted by UKCCIS, 60% of parents were not aware of these and less than 17% actively used them (Literature review by UKCCIS evidence group).&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;&#160;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;5-6 year olds report spending 1.4 hours per day on devices online&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;15-16 year olds reported spending an average of 4.4 hours per day&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;27% reported being able to turn off or get around parental controls&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;63% of teens surveyed say they know how to hide what they do online from their parents&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;54% said they would feel isolated if they couldn&amp;apos;t talk to friends online&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;(The figures are approximate and come from a selection of several studies)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Family Life and Technology&lt;u&gt; &lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;&#160;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt 18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;Schools increasingly communicate with parents electronically  through text, email and facebook pages.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt 18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt; Educational activities can be accessed online, providing parents with a way to get involved in the following ways; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt 18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Improving connectedness :-&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Parents can keep in contact with their children throughout the day/night. Knowing where they are and what time they are coming home. Children and young people can contact parents if they&amp;apos;re upset, have missed their bus etc. Facetime, WhatsApp and Skype provide a way of keeping in contact with extended family.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;When families are together however, studies show that technology may have the opposite impact. Parents and children are &amp;apos;plugged into&amp;apos; various devices, and leaving less time to interact with each other face to face. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;&#160;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Little research in the area, although there are anecdotal examples&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Parents passing on bad habits to their children.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Children feeling ignored&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Behaviours are then passed onto teenagers who in turn disengage from communicating with their family&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;An American study in 2016 found there was a strong correlation between the amount of time parents spent on social media and their parenting style&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Those parents who reported spending more time on social media, were found to have more authoritarian parenting styles  shouting or threatening consequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Parents who spent less time, by and large spent more time explaining things to their children&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;UK Safer Internet Centre  Digital Friendships Survey&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#160;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Snap chat and snap map&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Snap Map enables people to see exactly where you are on a map.&#160; It can be turned off, but young people are often not aware of the potential dangers of leaving it on.&#160; In extreme situations it can be used by unsafe adults, traffickers, paedophiles. Or coercive partners to track a person&amp;apos;s movements. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;A Snap story  runs alongside Snap Chat. This provides a stream of updates from people you follow, e.g. friends, family, celebrities/strangers &#160;which can often have very sexualised content. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Other media trends&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;&#160;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Yellow&lt;/strong&gt; is growing in popularity among school-age teens who use it to chat and send pictures to friends and strangers. It is similar to dating app&#160;Tinder&#160;in that it allows people to connect with others based on their location, with users &amp;apos;swiping&amp;apos; to accept or decline talking to someone based on their profile picture. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Whatsapp&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt; is an instant messaging application.&#160; Recently Whatsapp increased its recommended age for use to 16 years old.&#160; The app has access to the user&amp;apos;s contacts and allows them to direct message, share videos/images or even have phone calls or video calls with a friend or group. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Kik&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;is used for&#160;instant messaging.&#160;It allows its users to create a free account by email and password. Kik allows users to message friends with everything from photos and videos, to&#160;GIFs&#160;and emoticons.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt 18pt;&quot;&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt 18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Other media trends (cont.)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;&#160;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instagram&lt;/strong&gt;&#160;is a mobile photo-sharing application that allows users to share pictures and videos either publicly or privately on the service, as well as through a variety of other social networking platforms, such as Facebook and Twitter. &amp;apos;Instagram&#160;Direct&amp;apos; enables users to send private messages&#160;to another user. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Musical.ly&lt;/strong&gt; (also now known as TIKTOK) is an app that joins social networking and music together into a do-it-yourself video platform. Users can create, save and share videos. Videos typically show lip-syncing and dance routines. This app requires careful monitoring as there are high levels of sexual exploitation and cyber bullying within it. Users can like and comment on other peoples videos, and even remix them and share them on again. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Monkey &lt;/strong&gt;allows users to video chat with strangers for 10 seconds before moving onto the next person. They can add more time or add the person on Snapchat&#160;to continue the connection. Before connecting, teens will see the age and gender of the potential friend, and they can accept the video chat or not. The&#160;terms of service&#160;allow users aged 13 and older, but there&#39;s no verification of age.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Other media trends (cont.)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;&#160;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;apos;Sarahah&amp;apos;&lt;/strong&gt; is an anonymous feedback app that teens are using to pass anonymous digital notes to each other. The app lets you create a profile and works as an add-on to the popular social networking app Snapchat. Drawing upon the contact list on your phone, it lets you connect with friends and send anonymous comments to them. It also lets you search for users and send anonymous messages to them as well, even if you don&amp;apos;t know them. Users can choose not to have their name or profile picture appear in the app&amp;apos;s search or receive messages from unregistered users, but they must opt out to make this happen. If they don&amp;apos;t, the name and photo they use to register will appear if other users search for them.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Secret Piano &lt;/strong&gt;is a fake gaming application. The app requires the user to perform a certain set of keys on the piano before unlocking photos/videos and apps that they want to keep hidden from others. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mylol&lt;/strong&gt; is a site and mobile app aimed at teenagers for the purposes of social networking and dating. On a user&amp;apos;s profile, they can display information including pictures, sexual orientation, quiz questions, videos and interests.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

