&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;&#160;Research suggest that children and young people&amp;apos;s exposure to pornography can lead to the following; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
